Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是在此沉睡了千年的音律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,古代的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,守卫拼死地抵抗超乎了我的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,让我吃尽苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村长尽给我捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害我浪费了不少时间才收集到这音律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.02,0:00:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击村子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我让这家伙干的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了夺回失去的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃了那么多苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查明了这里的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爬上了镇长的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发掘出埋藏的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后骗取你们的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快告诉我剩下的音律在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拷问实在太浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实交待就让你死得痛快点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.41,0:01:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 还是直接杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.89,0:01:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再用秽土转生来逼供吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 你真了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你打败了晓的佩因
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我都败给他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我失去了力量 即便如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的陈年旧帐我没兴趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敢对大叔下手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些蛇会吞噬查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你越是增加查克拉量束缚得就越紧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还如此狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当自己是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…这个就是你们想要的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你们好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放了多克老师和鸣人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来音律在孩子们的手里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经在上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是鼓起勇气来救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:03:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兜 应该是分身…还有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是五个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪不在家…为什么来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之小心前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 别碰孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凑齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于凑齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凑齐七根了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能恢复力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查克拉…吞噬…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若想控制力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可用七段音律组合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照规定顺序启动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组合不同 力量释放的强弱亦不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手动操作可更新音律的输入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:06:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亦或七个时辰自动感知并更新
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音律组合若不合规定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,则保持更新前的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是对的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么如此乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想见…老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害 厉害 真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…天之矛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这就是启动的顺序…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么释放力量就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野心太强会自取灭亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这绝非人类可掌控之物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确认过以前的通缉令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经以为你丧生于晓的战斗里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅长通灵术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着上千条人命在手的杀人狂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还与大蛇丸一起研究禁术秽土转生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,束手就擒吧 迪索纳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下你们全完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井野 丁次…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好感受艺术的魅力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艺术就是…爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙要进行仪式…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须先写咒印才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们决不能让他有机可乘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…到底是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的…力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迄今为止…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从很多人身上学到很多重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个很厉害的人教会了我很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝非螺旋丸 仙术或是九尾的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:13:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐井
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秽土转生的忍者竟然没有复活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来被当作弃子了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于逮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的能力 没人协助是无法发挥的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怪就怪你那冗长复杂的准备过程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协助 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个会给人添麻烦的老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不会再让你乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事已至此…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能就此放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这算什么啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来组成你的克隆蛇有很大缺陷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力求快速成长的同时寿命却变短了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为防万一 我还准备了二十多个对策呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来用不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在不断崩解坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的地面是由树根支撑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶紧从巨坑脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 那个无法阻止吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那股笼罩世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会毁灭世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能沐浴在那股力量之下…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,想要守护 想要帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,最重要的人们 我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,相信正义的力量 相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.71,0:22:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:22:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,力量 最终章

